Package: gluey
Title: Markdown Text Generation with Enhanced Templates
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Robin", "Shannon", , "first.last@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Generate markdown text using the familiar syntax of 'glue'
    with enhanced templating features. Unlike 'cli' which produces styled
    console output, 'gluey' outputs plain markdown text, making it ideal
    for document generation in R Markdown and Quarto documents.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://github.com/vorpalvorpal/gluey
BugReports: https://github.com/vorpalvorpal/gluey/issues
